{"tid":758977,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【有咩陰謀？】政府倡行政方式分5G頻譜予電訊商","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T17:18:36.000Z","uid":36551,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"85cafa91414fe92b2d5691670f884f2a8faeb42e","tid":758977,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:41:20.000Z","msg":"政府倡行政方式分5G頻譜予電訊商<br />\n更新：2018/07/28 12:03<br />\n<br />\n政府建議新一批 5G 頻譜以行政方式分配予電訊商，無須競投，商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華指，這做法可節省業界成本，又相信 5G 服務收費不會過高。 <br />\n<br />\n5G 頻譜諮詢至下月底結束，政府建議不用競投方式將二十六及二十八「吉赫頻譜」，以極低價甚至免費分配給電訊商作 5G 用途。 <br />\n<br />\n那市民將來用 5G 服務是否可較便宜？商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華指，都是要靠市場競爭，但相信收費不會過高。 <br />\n<br />\n邱騰華指以行政方式分配頻譜，節省到競投的時間和成本，希望及早發展智慧城市，他又指， 5G 的網速比4G還要快至少十倍，加上低延誤的特點，可以發展無人駕駛汽車、遙控機械手術等，期望明年第一季完成分配，於二零二零年推出 5G 服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531711/即時新聞/政府倡行政方式分5G頻譜予電訊商\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531711%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%80%A1%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%865G%E9%A0%BB%E8%AD%9C%E4%BA%88%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E5%95%86&d=Qs%2FWYXSXxEG7f5jIpYGn3sP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=07e173f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F531711%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%80%A1%E8%A1%8C%E6%94%BF%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%865G%E9%A0%BB%E8%AD%9C%E4%BA%88%E9%9B%BB%E8%A8%8A%E5%95%86&h=40f58599\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/531711/即時新聞/政府倡行政方式分5G頻譜予電訊商</a><br />\n<br />\n1800/2100mhz頻譜政府又話收回拍賣可以加強競爭，高價競投唔會令電訊商加價<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=85169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D85169&d=Qs%2FWYXSXxEG7f5jIpYGn3sP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=7eb61fb5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D85169&h=9f196891\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=85169</a><br />\n而家又話要幫電訊商節省成本？<br />\n係咪支移冇錢投呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c5e643fe4bf8b3795248a34f200d27a68754cc","tid":758977,"uid":101555,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"係中資太多錢投 <br />\n幫緊本地公司嫁傻豬"},{"pid":"e580896c73982a5406af32b3d117fab1deda5076","tid":758977,"uid":108146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:50:29.000Z","msg":"平分？"},{"pid":"e88e7febacc72d6f7da3e13b5e213766bb3c3c6a","tid":758977,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"因為根本無乜人投<br />\n搞一大罉嘢都係人人底價投得<br />\n咁梗係直接分咗佢慳返場大龍鳳"},{"pid":"b7778de85b0cecc8671c0c2e85b8e09b84e82e31","tid":758977,"uid":36551,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"38c5e643fe4bf8b3795248a34f200d27a68754cc","tid":758977,"uid":101555,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"係中資太多錢投 <br />\n幫緊本地公司嫁傻豬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:53:01.000Z","msg":"我就唔信通訊局班仆街會幫本地電訊商<br />\n仲要前排HKT先開記者會屌政府5G政策有問題<br />\n會唔會咁順攤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccc66daf819b42a405920dbee8b20c6bec47b71","tid":758977,"uid":4964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:53:25.000Z","msg":"中移動或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"dbc0231c6903f6f2b246aab6257668957eeda4d6","tid":758977,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4f5efc963e0e6ec952eface5e733b5920f69fa8","tid":758977,"uid":73972,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b7778de85b0cecc8671c0c2e85b8e09b84e82e31","tid":758977,"uid":36551,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"38c5e643fe4bf8b3795248a34f200d27a68754cc","tid":758977,"uid":101555,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"cite